CustomField.description: Used for the mapValues rule. Defines the field on the output where the value will be mapped. A list of fields can be specified separating them with commas. The token "<<NS>>" can be used to replace it with the required namespace.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Defines the field on the output where the value will be mapped. A list of fields can be specified separating them with commas.
CustomField.label: Maps To
